What We Do

we're Helping redefine the way WordPress sites are managed and how content is curated.
our scalable, cloud-based solution breaks both of the most common barriers of entry to wordPress (technical & financial), keeping most Personal brands, businesses, & entrepreneurs from weilding the power of wordPress {y-WPaaS}, We empower self-starters through dI-y solutions, thus raising the percieved capacity of their ability in the tech space while and allowing them to define their brand's existence like never before using and finally unlock the limitless possibilities WordPress provides. 

01. Integrated WordPress Solution

At Y-Xist, we believe in simplicity, synergy, and synchronicity. That's why we've developed an integrated platform that combines managed WordPress hosting, top-tier premium plugins, and Do-It-Together {DIT} support services. Our approach ensures that every component of your WordPress site works seamlessly together, offering a hassle-free experience. This integration is a game-changer, setting us apart from competitors who might offer disjointed services.

02. ​Global Reach with Local Touch

Understanding the global nature of the web, Y-Xist uses Digital Ocean for hosting, offering a selection of data centers across the globe. This ensures your site is always close to your audience, reducing latency and improving performance. Our platform is equipped with features like staging, migration tools, and free SSLs, tailored for both the seasoned developer and the budding web entrepreneur.

03. ​​Powerful Plugins for Peak Performance

Our suite of pro plugins is designed to optimize, secure, and enhance your WordPress site. From Y-Smush's advanced image optimization to Y-Fly’s site speed improvements and Y-Defend's robust security features, we've got you covered. These plugins are not just add-ons; they are integral tools that elevate your website's performance.

04. ​​Value-Driven Pricing

Y-Xist offers a range of membership packages designed to provide maximum value. Whether you're a freelancer, an agency, or a business, our packages are tailored to your needs, offering unlimited access to our services and plugins. Our pricing reflects our commitment to providing an all-in-one solution that's more cost-effective than piecing together separate services.

05. Why Choose Y-Xist?

We encourage conducting your own head-to-head comparison with competitors current solutions in the market- we’re confident Y-Xist will consistently outperform in areas like SEO support, website security, and plugin quality. While others may have the edge in specific features, our holistic approach to WordPress management makes Y-Xist the wise choice for those who value an integrated, comprehensive solution.As you navigate the world of WordPress, let Y-Xist be your guide and partner. We're not just a service provider; we're your ally in the digital space, empowering you to achieve more with WordPress.Discover the Y-Xist difference today – where your WordPress journey meets innovation, integration, and impeccable support. Join us and experience the future of WordPress management.
